The Time Lord is back! And we're celebrating with a
Blue Peter Doctor Who special.

Lindsey goes behind the scenes on the brand new series
with our three competition winners to see their sonic
devices in action on set and meet Peter Capaldi himself.

We show you how to make your very own TARDIS T-shirt
and actor Dan Starkey, who plays Strax in the show, joins
us in studio to chat about the prosthetics involved in
making his character. It's out of this world!
